  "description": "Conversion of one self-contained flat on upper floors into three self-contained flats with provision of cycle storage; refuse storage; construction of part first floor and second floor rear extension (following demolition of existing rear additions); rear roof extension; rear outrigger roof extension; installation of three rooflights to front roofslope; alterations to rear fenestrations.",
